instructions.

Requirements:
For this project, you'll scrape this site, http://books.toscrape.com.
This CLI Data Gem program flow:

Scrape the books.toscrape site.

-A user should be presented with a list of Book GENERS to select from.

     -then select a genre, 


-they should then be presented with a list of book names from that genre.
     -The user should only see the first ten books, 
     -there should be an option for the user to either select from that list or see the next set of ten books.
     
-Select book to get the book names-

    - -- A user can then select a book and be given the books name
    ---- the Product description, and its product information.

  The user should be able to then see the book list again, 
start over or exit the gem.
The TC who you have been working with will provide support throughout this process.
